This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1080

This script maps xmms control functions to the following functionkeys:

F6        Decrease volume by 5%
F7        Increase volume by 5%
F8        Show title of currently playing song
F9        Open XMMS
S-F9    Close XMMS
F10      Start playing
S-F10  Stop playing
F11      Pause playing
S-F11  Toggle shuffle
F12      Play next
S-F12  Play previous
